oads/2024/09/the-weeknd-new-album-brazil.jpg" alt="周末" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-weeknd-new-album-brazil.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-weeknd-new-album-brazil-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-weeknd-new-album-brazil-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-weeknd-new-album-brazil-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-weeknd-new-album-brazil-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-weeknd-new-album-brazil-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3791680" class="wp-caption-text"> 2024 年 9 月 7 日，The Weeknd 在巴西圣保罗 MorumBIS 举行的“After Hours Til Dawn Tour”中登台表演。图片来源：Wagner Meier/Getty Images for Live Nation</figcaption></figure><p>上周末，他在圣保罗举办了一场音乐会，在那里他首次展示了全新的音乐、舞台设置和新的视觉效果，开创了他的新时代。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-what-the-weeknd-played-at-his-special-sao-paulo-concert-3791657">在这里查看他表演的完整列表。</a></p><p>在圣保罗演唱会之前，The Weeknd还在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-reveals-artwork-for-new-album-hurry-up-tomorrow-3791679">社交媒体上公布了《Hurry Up Tomorrow》的艺术作品</a>。它有一个简单的脸部特写镜头，与他“下班后”时代所见的面部假肢不同。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-dawn-fm-review-3132463">在对 2022 年《Dawn FM》的四星评论中</a>， <em>NME</em>写道，这张专辑“感觉像是 The Weeknd 寻找内心平静之旅的第一步；也许下次我们收到他的消息时，他就会完全拥抱曙光”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-walks-towards-the-light-in-new-dancing-in-the-flames-video-3793330">The Weeknd 在新的“Dancing In The Flames”视频中走向光明的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
